title: Chunga
description:
'Chunga'

B.T. Publishing, 1978, 66 pages

Written and Illustrated by Dante Volpe

Story titles; Chunga of Kaledon, Jafar The Cat, Paal, Yes

The cover reads...

Violent Quest For The She-Virgin

Erotic Butterfly Girls

Bisexual Amazons

The Primeval Brute

Honestly, it's probably not quite as good as that sounds, but it has a unique look and was a fun enough read.
